texts.text: No, I see two gods with you, too. What do you want?
See? Just like we told you, Lord Yoshitsune!
These humans came to smash this place up!
Whaa? Way to flip the script!
They're here to ruin our peaceful livesss!
We gotta beat 'em before they beat us!
Hold up, hold up! That's total BS!
I mean, props for thinking on your feet. But I call BS!
These villains even took out your beloved teacher!
Lord Kurama Tengu tried to protect our home, but... *sniff*
Yes, we'll avenge Lord Kurama Tengu!
If I cannot trust my own men, then who else is there!
I won't stand for it. I won't let anyone threaten our safe haven!
This demon mob is just using you!
But you will NOT insult my subordinates!
>Yoshitsune lunges but you react too late.
Even in life, you were guileless.
Some admired you for it, but more than a few did not.
As a leader, it is important to keep your heart and ears open.
I said it a thousand times, yet you never understood.
You speak like you know me.
Surely you have not forgotten it, Yoshitsune.
Takes me back. I owed you much as a mortal swordsman.
Why would you destroy this place?
This place for my followers and me.
You shouldn't have reason to create such a mess.
If you truly plan to invade the world above, I must stop you.
Oh my, he denied it in a heartbeat.
Then why's this place hoppin' with demons?
Like I said, they admire and follow me.
They followed me to their deaths. This place is for them.
I created it as a refuge for their souls.
But the number of newcomers has oddly multiplied.
In any case, I've done nothing wrong.
I swear, Hachiman, I'd never ruin the nation my brother united!
I see. Yoshitsune made this Aura Gate...
for the sake of his closest and loyal followers.
To give all to one's clan... That does sound like Yoshitsune.
Even in the end, Yoshitsune never had his own safe haven.
It is no surprise his desire for one intensified.
Is this what Kurama Tengu was tryin' to tell us?
The real source of mayhem is...
Now we know EXACTLY who to fight.
There's got to be some sort of mistake.
Guesss we can't hide it anymore.
But Yoshitsune'sss mighty power is oursss!
>An ominous cloud envelops the fake followers.
>A giant mass of evil rises up like a wall!
They're turning into a new demon!
No. They are trying to take a form but can only pulsate.
It is evidence of Yoshitsune's strength, that of purity.
With proximity to Yoshitsune, they took that immense power and...
Say your prayers! We're gonna kill you together!
They failed to take a shape and became a demonic abomination.
You're nothing! We'll crush your bones to dust!
>The Liberators jump out of the way and ready their phones.
Either these demons ravage the upper world,
or their evil stirs the Dragon Stream and hastens humanity's demise.
Eliminate all the demons here who harbor evil desires!
